com.adobe.fd.cpdf.api

Class ToImageOptionsSpec

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adobe.fd.cpdf.api.ToImageOptionsSpec
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class ToImageOptionsSpec
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Enables you to define run-time options that control how the Convert PDF service converts a PDF document to image files.To see this data type used in a code example, see the Converting a PDF document to JPEG files using the Java API quick start in Programming with LiveCycle ES.
    See Also:
